<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I beliieve his position on nuclear arms for Pakistan are consistent with his other statements on nuclear arms. Chomsky is not in favor of nuclear prol<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I beliieve his position on nuclear arms for Pakistan are consistent with his other statements on nuclear arms. Chomsky is not in favor of nuclear proliferation.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
